Dorrith Oppenheim was born in Kassel, Germany, in December 1938 to Hans and Trudi Oppenheim. Her parents were deported to #Auschwitz, where they died. https://t.co/sXpqhXfdOG
Prisoners who made it through the selection and incorporation into Auschwitz-Birkenau had their photos taken.
